<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="ISO-8859-1">
<title>Fillin Puzzles - Help</title>
</head>
<body>
	<h2>Fillin Puzzles - Help</h2>
	<h4>Home Page</h4>
	<ol>
		<li>Play Button
			<ul>
				<li>The Play button creates a new puzzle to play.</li>
				<li>The new puzzle is created and added as a tab to the vertical bar on the left of the screen.</li>
			</ul>
		</li>
		<li>Language Selector
			<ul>
				<li>The Language Selector determines the language for the next generated puzzle.</li>
			</ul>
		</li>
		<li>Summary Button
			<ul>
				<li>Presents the player's puzzle history and game progress.</li>
			</ul>
		</li>
		<li>? Button
			<ul>
				<li>Opens a help page that explains Fillin game functionality.</li>
			</ul>
		</li>
	</ol>
	<h4>Game Play</h4>
	<ol>
		<li>Title
			<ul>
				<li>Title of the puzzle.</li>
			</ul>
		</li>
		<li>Clues
			<ul>
				<li>Clues are displayed in a vertical list to the left of the puzzle grid.</li>
				<li>The clues are grouped by character length of the word.</li>
				<li>Click on the the letter group to view the words within the group.</li>
			</ul>
		</li>
		<li>Grid
			<ul>
				<li>Words are placed in white cells.</li>
				<li>Black cells in the grid are left unfilled.</li>
				<li>Words are placed vertically and horizontally.</li>
			</ul>
		</li>
		<li>Answer Entry
			<ul>
				<li>The puzzle grid accepts keyboard word entry.</li>
				<li>The clues can be selected and moved to the puzzle grid.
					<ul>
						<li>Select the word to be moved from the Clues area.</li>
						<li>Go to the puzzle grid.</li>
						<li>Click and drag the mouse cursor over the white spaces on the puzzle grid to place the word into the answer space.</li>
						<li>Click 'Insert' to insert the word into the answer space (if necessary).</li>
					</ul>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</li>
		<li>Next Button
			<ul>
				<li>The Next button skips over the current puzzle and generates another puzzle.</li>
			</ul>
		</li>
		<li>Language Selector
			<ul>
				<li>The Language Selector determines the language for the next generated puzzle.</li>
			</ul>
		</li>
		<li>? Button
			<ul>
				<li>Opens a help page that explains Fillin game functionality.</li>
			</ul>
		</li>
		<li>Print Button
			<ul>
				<li>Displays the puzzle in HTML for printing.</li>
			</ul>
		</li>
		<li>Submit Button
			<ul>
				<li>Submits the player's grid for answer verification.</li>
			</ul>
		</li>
	</ol>
</body>
</html>